Adadin wadanda suka mutu a tsunami a Indonesia ya haura zuwa 832
Adadin wadanda suka mutu a girgizar kasa da tsunami na Indonesia ya haura zuwa 832, hukumar bala'o'in kasar ta ce da sanyin safiya a ranar Lahadi.
Mutane da yawa sun kasance a tsare a cikin tarkace na gine-gine kawo saukar a 7.5 magnitude girgizar kasa wanda ya buga Jumma'a da kuma jawo raƙuman ruwa a matsayin high kamar yadda 20 feet, hukumar mai magana da yawun Sutopo Purwo Nugroho ya ce a wani taron manema labarai.
Birnin Palu, wanda ke da mutane fiye da 380,000, ya cika da tarkace daga gine-gine da suka rushe.
'Yan sanda sun kama wani mutum, mai shekara 32, bisa zargin kisan kai bayan da aka kashe matar da wuka
