Dutsen mai aman wuta ya zubo toka a kan Birnin Mexico
Ash yana fitowa daga dutsen Popocatepetl ya kai unguwannin kudancin babban birnin Mexico.
Cibiyar Kula da Bala'o'i ta Kasa ta gargadi 'yan Mexico a ranar Asabar da su nisanta kansu daga dutsen mai aman wuta bayan da aka fara aiki a cikin ramin kuma ya yi rikodin 183 na iskar gas da toka a cikin awanni 24.
Cibiyar tana sa ido kan yawan tsawa da girgizar kasa.
Hotuna a shafukan sada zumunta sun nuna matattarar murfin toka a kan gilashin mota a unguwannin Mexico City kamar Xochimilco.
Masana ilimin kimiyyar ƙasa sun lura da ƙaruwar aiki a dutsen mai fitad da wuta wanda ke da nisan mil 45 (kilomita 72) kudu maso gabashin babban birnin tun lokacin da girgizar ƙasa mai girman 7.1 ta girgiza tsakiyar Mexico a watan Satumbar 2017.
Dutsen mai suna "Don Goyo" ya fara aiki tun daga shekara ta 1994.
'Yan sanda sun yi arangama da 'yan awaren Catalonia a gabannin ranar tunawa da zaben' yancin kai
An kama mutane shida a Barcelona a ranar Asabar bayan masu zanga-zangar neman 'yanci sun yi karo da 'yan sanda masu tayar da tarzoma, kuma yayin da dubbai suka shiga zanga-zangar adawa don bikin cika shekaru daya da kada kuri'ar raba gardama ta Catalonia kan rabuwa.
Wasu gungun masu neman rabuwa da ke rufe fuska da 'yan sandan suka hana su yin zanga-zanga sun yi musu kazafi da kuma zubar da fenti, suna haifar da duhu mai duhu a kan tituna da yawanci za su cika da yawon bude ido.
Har ila yau, an yi ta gwagwarmaya a cikin rana tare da 'yan sanda ta amfani da sandunansu don magance fadace-fadace.
A cikin sa'o'i da yawa ƙungiyoyin masu fafutukar 'yancin kai suna rera "Babu mantuwa, babu gafara" sun fuskanci masu zanga-zangar ƙungiyar da ke ihu, "Long live Spain".
Mutane goma sha huɗu sun sami magani don ƙananan raunin da suka samu a cikin zanga-zangar, jaridar gida ta ruwaito.
Rikici ya kasance mai ƙarfi a cikin yankin mai son 'yancin kai shekara guda bayan zaben raba gardama na 1 ga Oktoba wanda Madrid ta ɗauka ba bisa doka ba amma' yan separatists Catalans sun yi bikin.
Masu jefa kuri'a sun zabi mafi rinjaye don zama 'yanci, kodayake yawan masu halartar ya kasance ƙasa da waɗanda ke adawa da rabuwa da ƙuri'a.
A cewar hukumomin Catalan kusan mutane 1000 sun ji rauni a bara bayan 'yan sanda sun yi kokarin dakatar da zabe a cibiyoyin zabe a fadin yankin a cikin rikice-rikice masu karfi.
Kungiyoyin 'yanci sun yi zango a daren ranar Juma'a don hana zanga-zangar goyon baya ga 'yan sandan kasa.
Zanga-zangar ta ci gaba amma an tilasta ta bi wata hanya.
Narcis Termes, mai shekaru 68, wani mai aikin lantarki wanda ya halarci zanga-zangar 'yan tawaye tare da matarsa ya ce ba shi da fata game da damar da Catalonia ke samu na samun' yanci.
"A shekarar da ta gabata mun yi rayuwa daya daga cikin mafi kyawun lokutanmu.
Na kalli iyayena suna kuka da farin ciki a kan samun damar yin zabe amma yanzu mun makale, "in ji shi.
Duk da samun gagarumar nasara a zaben yanki a watan Disamba da ya gabata, jam'iyyun Catalonia masu neman 'yancin kai sun yi gwagwarmaya don ci gaba da ci gaba a wannan shekara tare da yawancin sanannun shugabanninsu a cikin gudun hijira ko a cikin tsare suna jiran shari'a saboda rawar da suka taka wajen shirya kuri'ar raba gardama da kuma sanarwar samun' yancin kai.
Joan Puig, wani mai aikin makaniki mai shekaru 42 da ke rikodin zanga-zangar goyon bayan 'yan sanda a wayar sa, ya ce 'yan siyasa a bangarorin biyu ne suka haifar da rikicin.
Ya ce, "Ya zama daɗaɗa damuwa".
A ranar Asabar, Oriol Junqueras, daya daga cikin shugabannin Catalan tara da ke cikin kurkuku tun daga karshen shekarar da ta gabata, ya sanar da cewa zai yi takara a zaben majalisar Turai a shekara mai zuwa.
"Tsaya takara a zaben na Turai shi ne hanya mafi kyau don nuna rashin amincewar dabi'un dimokiradiyya da kuma matsi da muka gani daga gwamnatin Spain", in ji shi.
