Lee, wanda littafinsa "AI Superpowers: China, Silicon Valley da New World Order" ya fito a wannan watan ta Houghton Mifflin Harcourt, shi ne Shugaba na Sinovation Ventures, wanda ya zuba jari a daya daga cikin shahararrun kamfanonin AI a China, Face ++.
A shekarun 1980 a Jami'ar Carnegie Mellon ya yi aiki a kan tsarin AI wanda ya doke mafi girman dan wasan Amurka na Othello, kuma daga baya ya kasance mai zartarwa a Microsoft Research kuma shugaban reshen Google na China.
Lee ya yarda da gasar fasahar gwamnatin Amurka ta baya kamar Hukumar Tsaro ta Cibiyar Bincike ta Tsaro ta Tsaro ta Robotics Challenge kuma ta tambayi lokacin da za a sake zama, don taimakawa wajen gano masu hangen nesa na gaba.
