LeBron zai yi Lakers farko Lahadi a San Diego
Jiran ya kusa karewa ga magoya baya da ke son ganin LeBron James ya fara buga wasan farko a kungiyar Los Angeles Lakers.
Kocin Lakers Luke Walton ya sanar da cewa James zai buga wasan farko na ranar Lahadi da Denver Nuggets a San Diego.
