Lokacin Taron Ranar Virginia na Yammacin Trump, Tashar YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump ya fara gangamin yakin neman zabe a daren yau a Wheeling, West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne na farko daga cikin gangamin da Trump zai yi a mako mai zuwa, wanda ya hada da tsayawa a wurare da ke da alaka da kasar, ciki har da Tennessee da Mississippi.
Tare da tabbatar da kuri'un da aka yi a kan zaɓaɓɓen sa don cike gurbin Kotun Koli, Trump yana da burin gina goyon baya ga za ~ en za ~ en tsakiyar za ~ en da ke zuwa tun lokacin da 'yan Republican ke cikin hadarin rasa ikon Majalisa lokacin da aka jefa kuri'u a ranar Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne taron gangamin Trump na West Virginia a daren yau kuma ta yaya kake kallon ta yanar gizo?
An shirya taron Trump na Wheeling, West Virginia a karfe 7 na yammacin ET a daren yau, Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Kuna iya kallon taron Trump na West Virginia a layi a ƙasa ta hanyar watsawa ta YouTube.
Trump na iya yin jawabi a zaman wannan makon na wanda aka zaba a kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya zama mai wahala a kan zargin cin zarafin jima'i tare da sa ran za a yi zaben tabbatar da majalisar dattijai har zuwa mako guda yayin da FBI ke gudanar da bincike.
Amma babban burin wannan gangamin na gangamin shi ne taimakawa 'yan Republican da ke fuskantar zaben Nuwamba na samun wani ci gaba.
Don haka, yakin neman zaben Shugaba Trump ya ce wadannan gangami biyar a mako mai zuwa suna da nufin "karfafawa masu sa kai da magoya baya yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da fadada rinjayen da suke da shi a Majalisar Dattijai da Majalisar Wakilai", a cewar Reuters.
"Sarrafa Majalisa na da muhimmanci ga ajandar sa har shugaban zai yi tafiya zuwa jihohi da dama kamar yadda zai yiwu yayin da muke shiga lokacin yakin neman zabe", wani mai magana da yawun kamfen din Trump wanda ya ki a bayyana sunansa ya fadawa Reuters.
An shirya taron yau da yamma a filin wasan Wesbanco a Wheeling, taron na yau da dare zai iya kawo magoya baya daga "Ohio da Pennsylvania da kuma jawo ɗaukar hoto daga kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh", a cewar West Virginia Metro News.
Ranar Asabar za ta kasance karo na biyu a cikin watan da ya gabata da Trump ya ziyarci West Virginia, jihar da ya lashe fiye da kashi 40 cikin ɗari a cikin 2016.
Trump na kokarin taimakawa dan takarar Sanata na Jam'iyyar Republican na Yammacin Virginia Patrick Morrisey, wanda ke bin bayan zabe.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ga Morrisey cewa shugaban ya zo ya yi kokarin ba shi kwarin gwiwa a zaben", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin kimiyyar siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
Ryder Cup 2018: Kungiyar Amurka ta nuna karfin gwiwa don gwagwarmaya don ci gaba da fatan rayuwa a cikin 'yan wasa na ranar Lahadi
Bayan zaman zaman guda uku, hutun da aka yi a ranar Asabar da yamma ya zama abin da wannan gasar Ryder ta bukata.
Gwanin motsi mai motsi cikakkiyar ra'ayi ce ta wasanni amma wacce 'yan wasa suka yi imani da gaske, kuma ba ta taɓa yin hakan ba kamar a gasa kamar waɗannan.
To a ina za su ce halin da ake ciki yanzu?
"Suna da maki shida da kuma yanzu yana da hudu, don haka muna dauke da cewa a matsayin kadan daga halin da ake ciki na tsammani", ya ce Jordan Spieth kamar yadda ya strolled kashe ga rana.
Turai na da fifiko, ba shakka, maki hudu a gaba tare da karin maki goma sha biyu a wasa.
Amurkawa, kamar yadda Spieth ya ce, suna jin cewa suna da iska a cikin jirgin su duk da haka kuma suna da abubuwa da yawa da za su karfafa gwiwa, ba ma na Spieth da Justin Thomas ba wanda ya taka leda tare duk rana kuma kowannensu yana alfahari da maki uku daga hudu.
Spieth ya kasance mai kisa daga tee zuwa kore kuma yana jagorantar misali.
Waɗannan kururuwan murna na murna sun yi ƙarfi yayin da zagayensa ya ci gaba, yana nutsewa a cikin mahimmin abu don ɗaukar wasa huɗu a fili lokacin da shi da Thomas suka kasance biyu bayan biyu.
Hukuncinsa da ya lashe wasan a 15 ya hadu da irin wannan ihu, irin wanda ya gaya maka cewa ya yi imanin cewa tawagar Amurka ba ta fita daga wannan ba.
"Dole ne ku yi zurfin zurfi da damuwa game da wasanku", in ji Spieth.
Wannan shi ne duk abin da kowane daga cikin waɗannan 'yan wasan ya bar yanzu.
18 ramuka don yin alama.
'Yan wasa guda daya da suka fi Spieth da Thomas maki a cikin kwanaki biyu da suka gabata su ne Francesco Molinari da Tommy Fleetwood, labarin da ba a iya jayayya ba na Ryder Cup.
Ƙasar Turai ta ban mamaki amma kyakkyawa biyu ne hudu daga hudu kuma ba zai iya yin kuskure ba.
"Moliwood" sune kawai ba su harba bogey a ranar Asabar da yamma ba, amma sun kuma kauce wa bogey a ranar Asabar da safe, Jumma'a da yamma da kuma baya tara a ranar Juma'a da safe.
Wannan gudu, da kuma yadda makamansu suke gudana duka zuwa da kuma daga wannan taron jama'a masu tsaurin ra'ayi suna tabbatar da cewa su ne 'yan wasan da za su doke ranar Lahadi, kuma ba za a sami wani dan wasa da ya fi shahara ba don rufe nasarar Turai mai yiwuwa yayin da rana ke faɗuwa a kan Le Golf National fiye da Fleetwood ko Molinari.
Zai fi dacewa duka biyu a lokaci guda a kan ramukan daban-daban.
Magana game da ɗaukakar Turai har yanzu ba ta da wuri.
Bubba Watson da Webb Simpson sun yi gajeren aiki na Sergio Garcia, gwarzon 'yan wasa na safe, lokacin da aka haɗa shi da Alex Noren.
Bogey da biyu biyu a gaban tara suka haƙa da Spaniard da Swede a cikin rami ba su taɓa samun kusa da hawa daga.
Amma a ranar Lahadi, ba wanda zai taimake ka ka fita daga ramin.
Kwallan kwallaye huɗu da kwallaye huɗu suna da ban sha'awa sosai don kallo sosai saboda hulɗar da ke tsakanin nau'i-nau'i, shawarar da suke bayarwa, shawarar da ba su bayar da kuma yadda dabarun za ta iya canzawa a cikin ɗan lokaci.
Turai ta taka rawar gani a matsayin kungiya har zuwa yanzu kuma ta jagoranci jagoranci zuwa ranar karshe amma wannan zaman na hudu ya nuna cewa Team USA tana da ciki don yakin da wasu, musamman Stateside, suka yi shakku.
Turai ta dauki 10-6 ta jagoranci zuwa Ryder Cup ranar karshe
Turai za ta yi amfani da lafiya a ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder bayan fitowa daga ranar Asabar da hudu da hudu da kuma wasanni na gida tare da 10-6 a kan Amurka.
Ƙwararrun 'yan wasa Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari sun jagoranci cajin tare da nasara biyu a kan Tiger Woods da ke fama da shan wahala don ɗaukar jimillarsu har yanzu a Le Golf National zuwa maki huɗu.
Thomas Bjorn na Turai, wanda ke neman ya ci gaba da cin kofin da suka rasa a Hazeltine shekaru biyu da suka gabata, ya mamaye wani bangare na Amurka da ke da mummunan rauni a cikin safiya hudu, ya dauki jerin 3-1.
Amurka ta ba da juriya a cikin ƙungiya huɗu, ta ci wasanni biyu, amma ba za su iya cinye rashi ba.
Kungiyar Jim Furyk na bukatar maki takwas daga wasannin guda 12 na ranar Lahadi don rike kofin.
Fleetwood shine farkon rookie na Turai don lashe maki hudu a jere yayin da shi da Molinari, wanda aka fi sani da "Molliwood" bayan karshen mako mai ban mamaki sune kawai biyu biyu don lashe maki hudu daga wasannin farko na hudu a tarihin Ryder Cup.
Bayan sun murkushe Woods da Patrick Reed a cikin kwallaye huɗu sai suka yi farin ciki sosai don doke Woods da ɗan asalin Amurka Bryson Dechambeau da ƙarin ƙarfafawa 5 & 4.
Woods, wanda ya jawo kansa ta hanyar wasanni biyu a ranar Asabar, ya nuna wasu lokuta na haske amma yanzu ya rasa 19 daga cikin wasanninsa 29 a cikin hudu da hudu da bakwai a jere.
Justin Rose, ya huta don wasan ƙwallon safiya, ya koma abokin Henrik Stenson a cikin foursomes zuwa 2 da 1 na Dustin Johnson da Brooks Koepka - wanda aka zaba a matsayi na ɗaya da na uku a duniya.
Turai ba ta da wata hanyar da za ta iya yin hakan a ranar da ta dace, a kudu maso yammacin Paris.
Mai nasara sau uku Jordan Spieth da Justin Thomas sun kafa misali ga Amurkawa da maki biyu a ranar Asabar.
Sun sami nasara 2 & 1 nasara a kan Jon Rahm na Spain da Ian Poulter a cikin kwallaye huɗu kuma sun dawo daga baya don doke Poulter da Rory McIlroy 4 & 3 a cikin masu wasa huɗu bayan sun rasa ramuka biyu na farko.
Sau biyu kawai a tarihin Ryder Cup wata kungiya ta dawo daga rashin maki hudu ta shiga cikin 'yan wasa, kodayake a matsayin masu rike da Furyk's gefen kawai suna bukatar zana don riƙe kofin.
Bayan kasancewa na biyu mafi kyau na kwana biyu, duk da haka, a ranar Lahadi da za a kai hari a ranar Lahadi kamar dai ba zai wuce su ba.
Koriya ta Arewa ta ce 'babu yadda' za ta kwance makamai a gefe daya ba tare da amincewa ba
Ministan harkokin wajen Koriya ta Arewa ya shaida wa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a ranar Asabar cewa ci gaba da takunkumi yana zurfafa rashin amincewa da Amurka kuma babu wata hanyar da kasar za ta daina barin makaman nukiliyarta a cikin irin wannan yanayi.
Ri Yong Ho ya fadawa babban taron shekara-shekara na kungiyar duniya cewa Koriya ta Arewa ta dauki "matakan kyawawan manufa" a shekarar da ta gabata, kamar dakatar da gwajin nukiliya da makamai masu linzami, rushe wurin gwajin nukiliya, da kuma yin alkawarin ba za a yada makaman nukiliya da fasahar nukiliya ba.
"Duk da haka, ba mu ga wani amsa mai dacewa daga Amurka ba", in ji shi.
"Ba tare da wani amincewa a Amurka ba za a sami amincewa a cikin tsaron kasa da kuma a karkashin irin wannan yanayi babu yadda za mu yi mu kwance makamai da kanmu".
Duk da yake Ri ya sake maimaita sanannun korafe-korafen Koriya ta Arewa game da juriya ta Washington ga tsarin "matakai" zuwa ga denuclearization wanda za a ba Koriya ta Arewa lada yayin da ta ɗauki matakai a hankali, jawabinsa ya bayyana da mahimmanci a cikin cewa ba ya ƙi ƙin ƙin nukiliya mai ƙarfi kamar yadda Pyongyang ya yi a baya.
Ri ya yi magana ne game da wata sanarwa ta hadin gwiwa da Kim Jong Un da Donald Trump suka fitar a taron farko tsakanin shugaban Amurka mai aiki da shugaban Koriya ta Arewa a Singapore a ranar 12 ga Yuni, lokacin da Kim ya yi alkawarin yin aiki don "hana makamin nukiliya na yankin Koriya " yayin da Trump ya yi alkawarin ba da tabbacin tsaron Koriya ta Arewa.
Koriya ta Arewa ta nemi a kawo karshen yakin Koriya na 1950-53, amma Amurka ta ce dole ne Pyongyang ta fara watsar da makaman nukiliya.
Washington ta kuma yi tsayayya da kira na sassauta tsauraran takunkumin kasa da kasa kan Koriya ta Arewa.
"Amurka ta dage kan" denuclearization-first "kuma ta kara matakin matsin lamba ta hanyar takunkumi don cimma manufar su ta hanyar tilastawa, har ma da yin adawa da" sanarwar karshen yaki, "" in ji Ri.
"Gaskiyar cewa takunkumi na iya sa mu durƙusa mafarki ne na mutanen da ba su san mu ba.
Amma matsalar ita ce ci gaba da takunkumi yana zurfafa rashin amincewarmu".
Ri bai ambaci shirin taron kolin na biyu tsakanin Kim da Trump da shugaban Amurka ya nuna a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a farkon makon ba.
Maimakon haka, ministan ya nuna tarurruka uku tsakanin Kim da shugaban Koriya ta Kudu Moon Jae-in a cikin watanni biyar da suka gabata kuma ya kara da cewa: "Idan jam'iyyar da ke cikin wannan batun batun kawar da makaman nukiliya ita ce Koriya ta Kudu kuma ba Amurka ba, da kawar da makaman nukiliya na yankin Koriya ba zai zo irin wannan ba".
Duk da haka, sautin jawabin Ri ya sha bamban da na bara, lokacin da ya fadawa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa harin da aka kai wa Amurka da rokoki na Koriya ta Arewa ba makawa bayan "Mr.
A wannan shekara a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, Trump, wanda a bara ya yi barazanar "halaka" Koriya ta Arewa, ya yaba wa Kim saboda ƙarfin hali wajen ɗaukar matakai don kwance makamai, amma ya ce har yanzu akwai sauran aiki da yawa da za a yi kuma dole ne a ci gaba da takunkumi har sai Koriya ta Arewa ta kawar da makaman nukiliya.
A ranar Laraba, Trump ya ce ba shi da lokacin da zai yi hakan, yana cewa "Idan ya ɗauki shekaru biyu, shekaru uku ko watanni biyar - ba kome".
Kasar Sin da Rasha sun yi jayayya cewa Kwamitin Tsaro na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ya kamata ya ba da lada ga Pyongyang saboda matakan da aka dauka.
Amma, sakataren harkokin wajen Amurka Mike Pompeo ya shaida wa kwamitin sulhun Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a ranar Alhamis cewa: "Dole ne a ci gaba da aiwatar da takunkumin kwamitin sulhu da karfi ba tare da gazawa ba har sai mun cimma cikakkiyar, karshe, tabbatar da kwashe makaman nukiliya".
Kwamitin Tsaro ya yi maraba da takunkumi kan Koriya ta Arewa tun 2006 a kokarin da yake yi na hana kudaden da ake bayarwa don shirin nukiliya da makaman nukiliya na Pyongyang.
Pompeo ya sadu da Ri a yayin taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya kuma ya ce daga baya zai sake ziyartar Pyongyang a watan gobe don shirya taron koli na biyu.
Pompeo ya ziyarci Koriya ta Arewa sau uku a wannan shekara, amma tafiyarsa ta ƙarshe ba ta yi kyau ba.
Ya bar Pyongyang a watan Yuli yana mai cewa an samu ci gaba, sai dai Koriya ta Arewa a cikin 'yan sa'o'i don ta la'ance shi saboda "buƙatar masu aikata laifi".
Koriya ta Arewa ta yi alkawari a wani taro da Moon a wannan watan don rushe wani rukunin makamai da makaman nukiliya idan Amurka ta dauki "matakan da suka dace".
Ya ce Kim ya gaya masa cewa "matakan da suka dace" da yake nema sun kasance tabbacin tsaro da Trump ya yi alkawarinsa a Singapore da kuma motsawa zuwa daidaita dangantakar da Washington.
Ɗaliban Harvard sun yi nazarin samun isasshen hutu
Wani sabon kwas a Jami'ar Harvard a wannan shekara ya sa duk ɗalibanta na digiri na farko su sami karin barci a ƙoƙarin yaƙi da al'adun macho na yin karatu ta hanyar 'kowane-dare' da ke cike da maganin kafeyin.
Wani masani ya gano cewa ɗalibai a jami'a mafi girma a duniya ba sa sanin ainihin abin da ya kamata su yi don su kula da kansu.
Charles Czeisler, farfesa a likitancin bacci a Harvard Medical School kuma kwararre a Brigham da Asibitin Mata, ya tsara wannan darasin, wanda ya yi imanin shi ne na farko a irin wannan a Amurka.
Ya yi wannan karatun ne bayan ya ba da jawabi game da tasirin rashin bacci a kan koyo.
'A ƙarshe wata yarinya ta zo wurina ta ce: 'Me ya sa aka gaya mini wannan yanzu, a shekarar da na gama makaranta?'
Ta ce babu wanda ya taɓa gaya mata game da muhimmancin bacci - wanda ya ba ni mamaki, 'ya gaya wa The Telegraph.
Wannan darasi, wanda aka fara shi a wannan shekarar, ya bayyana wa dalibai muhimman abubuwan da yadda barci mai kyau ke taimakawa a karatunsu da kuma wasan motsa jiki, da kuma inganta lafiyarsu gaba daya.
Paul Barreira, farfesa a fannin ilimin halayyar kwakwalwa a Makarantar Likita ta Harvard kuma babban daraktan kula da lafiyar jami'ar, ya ce jami'ar ta yanke shawarar gabatar da karatun bayan gano dalibai suna fama da rashin bacci a cikin mako.
Darasin na tsawon sa'a guda ya ƙunshi jerin ayyuka masu ban sha'awa.
A wani bangare akwai hoton dakin dakuna, inda dalibai ke danna kofuna na kofi, labule, masu horo da littattafai don a gaya musu game da tasirin maganin kafeyin da haske da kuma yadda rashin bacci ke shafar wasan motsa jiki, da kuma mahimmancin tsarin bacci.
A wani sashe, an gaya wa mahalarta yadda rashin barci na dogon lokaci zai iya kara hadarin bugun zuciya, bugun jini, damuwa da kuma ciwon daji.
Taswirar harabar, tare da gumaka masu ma'amala, sannan yana ƙarfafa mahalarta suyi tunani game da ayyukansu na yau da kullun.
'Mun san ba zai canza halayen ɗalibai nan da nan ba.
Amma mun yi imanin suna da hakkin sanin hakan - kamar yadda kuke da hakkin sanin illar shan sigari ga lafiyarku", in ji Farfesa Czeisler.
Al'adun alfahari a cikin 'ja da baya' har yanzu yana wanzuwa, in ji shi, yana mai cewa fasahar zamani da kuma ƙara yawan matsin lamba a kan ɗalibai na nufin rashin bacci ya zama matsala mai girma.
Tabbatar da cewa kuna da isasshen bacci, mai inganci, ya kamata ya zama 'makamin sirri' na ɗalibi don yaƙar damuwa, gajiya da damuwa, in ji shi - har ma don kauce wa yin nauyi, kamar yadda rashin bacci ke sanya kwakwalwa cikin yanayin yunwa, yana sa su ci gaba da jin yunwa.
Raymond So, dan shekara 19 dan California mai karatun kimiyyar kimiya da kimiyyar halitta, ya taimaka wa Farfesa Czeisler tsara kwas ɗin, ya halarci ɗayan darasinsa a shekarar da ta gabata a shekararsa ta farko a Harvard.
Ya ce wannan karatun ya buɗe masa ido kuma ya sa ya matsa lamba don yin karatun a duk harabar makarantar.
Mataki na gaba, yana fatan, shi ne ya nemi duk daliban digiri na biyu su kammala irin wannan shirin karatu kafin shiga cibiyar gasa.
Farfesa Czeisler ya ba da shawarar cewa ɗalibai su yi la'akari da saita agogon ƙararrawa don lokacin da za su yi barci, da kuma lokacin da za su tashi, kuma su kasance da masaniya game da illolin 'hasken shuɗi' da allon lantarki da hasken LED ke fitarwa, wanda zai iya jefa yanayin circadian ku daga kilter, yana haifar da matsaloli na barci.
Livingston 1 - 0 Rangers: Manufar Menga ta kashe mutanen Gerrard
Rangers sun sake shan wahala a ranar da Dolly Menga ta yi wa Steven Gerrard kwallo a wasan da suka yi nasara da ci 1-0 a Livingston.
Kungiyar Ibrox na neman yin rikodin nasarar su ta farko a kan hanya tun bayan nasarar da suka yi a watan Fabrairu 4-1 a St Johnstone, amma kungiyar Gary Holt ta yi wa Gerrard kashi na biyu ne kawai a wasanni 18 a matsayin koci don barin kungiyarsa maki takwas a kan manyan shugabannin Ladbrokes Hearts.
Menga ya buga minti bakwai kafin a tashi daga wasan kuma tawagar Rangers ba ta da ƙarfin yin hakan.
Yayin da Rangers suka sauka zuwa matsayi na shida, Livingston ya hau zuwa na uku kuma kawai a bayan Hibernian a kan bambancin burin.
Kuma za a iya samun karin matsala a cikin shagon ga Rangers bayan da aka kula da Calum Spence na layi don ciwon kai bayan an jefa wani abu daga ƙarshen ƙarshen.
Gerrard ya yi sauye-sauye takwas a bangaren da ya wuce Ayr zuwa wasan kusa da na karshe na gasar Betfred.
Holt, a gefe guda, ya tafi tare da wannan Livi 11 wanda ya ɗauki maki daga Hearts a makon da ya gabata kuma zai yi farin ciki da yadda yadda aka yi masa kyau ya yi wa abokan hamayyarsu a kowane lokaci.
Yan Rangers sun yi amfani da kwallon amma Livingston ya yi amfani da kwallon da suke da shi.
Ya kamata su ci kwallaye biyu kawai lokacin da aka fara buga wasan Menga ya aika da Scott Pittman ta hanyar Allan McGregor amma dan wasan tsakiya ya yi amfani da babbar damarsa.
Keaghan Jacobs ya buga kwallo mai zurfi sannan ya sami kyaftin Craig Halkett amma abokin aikinsa na kare Alan Lithgow zai iya yin harbi ne kawai a baya.
'Yan Rangers sun yi nasarar kama iko amma akwai fata fiye da imani game da wasan su a kashi na uku na karshe.
Alfredo Morelos tabbas ya ji ya kamata ya sami hukunci a alamar sa'a na huɗu kamar yadda shi da Steven Lawless suka yi karo amma alƙali Steven Thomson ya yi watsi da roko na Colombian.
Rangers sun sami nasarar harbi biyu ne kawai a farkon rabin lokaci amma tsohon mai tsaron gidan Ibrox Liam Kelly bai damu da bugun kawunan Lassana Coulibaly da bugun Ovie Ejaria ba.
Duk da cewa wasan farko da Livi ya buga a minti na 34 na wasan zai iya zama a kan tsarin wasan, babu wanda zai iya musun cewa sun cancanci hakan saboda kwazon da suka yi.
Kuma Rangers sun kasa magance wani abu mai zurfi na Jacobs.
Scott Arfield bai amsa ba kamar yadda Declan Gallagher ya jefa kwallon zuwa Scott Robinson, wanda ya ci gaba da kasancewa mai hankali don zaɓar Menga don kammala sauƙi.
Gerrard ya yi aiki a lokacin hutu yayin da ya canza Coulibaly don Ryan Kent kuma sauyawar ta kusan samar da tasiri nan da nan yayin da mai tsaron ragar ya shiga cikin Morelos amma Kelly mai ban sha'awa ya yi tsere daga layinsa zuwa toshewa.
Amma Livingston ya ci gaba da tsotse baƙi a cikin wasa daidai irin wasan da suke jin daɗi, tare da Lithgow da Halkett suna yin ƙwallon ƙwallon ƙwallon ƙwallon ƙafa.
Kungiyar Holt ta iya karawa da ta jagoranci a matakai na karshe amma McGregor ya tsaya da kyau don ya hana Jacobs kafin Lithgow ya kai gaba daga kusurwa.
Sauran Rangers Glenn Middleton yana da wani lokacin da ya yi ikirarin cewa ya yi hukunci yayin da ya yi rikici da Jacobs amma kuma Thomson ya dubi baya.
Almanac: Wanda ya ƙirƙiro na'urar ƙidayar Geiger
Kuma yanzu shafi daga "Sunday Morning" Almanac: Satumba 30, 1882, shekaru 136 da suka wuce a yau, kuma kirgawa ... ranar da aka haifi masanin kimiyyar lissafi na gaba Johannes Wilhelm "Hans" Geiger a Jamus.
Geiger ya ƙirƙiro wata hanya ta auna ƙarfin rediyo, kuma hakan ya sa aka ƙera na'urar da ake kira Geiger Counter.
Babban jigon kimiyya tun daga lokacin, Geiger Counter ya zama babban jigon al'adun gargajiya, kamar yadda yake a fim din 1950 "Bells of Coronado", wanda ya hada da wadanda suka kasance masu binciken kimiyyar da ba za su iya ba Roy Rogers da Dale Evans:
Mutumin: "Mene ne wannan?"
Rogers: "Kayan aikin Geiger ne, wanda ake amfani da shi wajen gano ma'adanai masu rediyo, kamar uranium.
Idan ka saka waɗannan na'urar sauraron kunne, za ka iya jin tasirin abubuwan da ke fitowa daga cikin ma'adanai".
Evans: "Ka ce, yana da gaske yanzu!"
"Hans" Geiger ya mutu a 1945, 'yan kwanaki kafin ranar haihuwarsa ta shekara 63.
Amma abin da ya ƙirƙiro ya ci gaba da rayuwa.
Sabon maganin kansa zai iya koya wa tsarin garkuwar jiki ya 'ga' ƙwayoyin cuta
Sabon maganin cutar kansa zai iya koya wa tsarin garkuwar jiki ya 'gan' ƙwayoyin cuta kuma ya kashe su
Alurar rigakafi tana koyar da tsarin garkuwar jiki ya gane ƙwayoyin da ba su dace ba a matsayin wani ɓangare na magani
Hanyar ta kunshi cire kwayoyin garkuwar jiki daga mai haƙuri, canza su a dakin gwaje-gwaje
Za su iya 'ganin' wani furotin da ke da yawa ga cututtuka da yawa sannan kuma a sake shigar da shi
Wani gwajin rigakafin yana nuna kyakkyawan sakamako a cikin marasa lafiya da ke da nau'ikan ciwon daji.
Wata mata da aka yi wa allurar, wadda take koya wa tsarin garkuwar jiki ya gane ƙwayoyin cuta, ta ga ciwon da ke jikinta ya ɓace na fiye da watanni 18.
Hanyar ta kunshi cire kwayoyin garkuwar jiki daga mai cutar, a canza su a dakin gwaje-gwaje domin su iya "ganin" wani furotin da ke tattare da cututtukan kansa da yawa da ake kira HER2, sannan a sake shigar da kwayoyin.
Farfesa Jay Berzofsky, na Ƙungiyar Kula da Ciwon Rashin Lafiya ta Amirka a Bethesda, Maryland, ya ce: "Sakamakon da muka samu ya nuna cewa muna da maganin da zai iya magance cutar".
HER2 "yana haifar da ci gaban nau'ikan cutar kansa da yawa", gami da nono, ovarian, huhu da kuma kansar hanji, in ji Farfesa Berzofsky.
Irin wannan tsarin da ake yi na ɗaukan ƙwayoyin cuta daga jikin marasa lafiya da kuma "koyar" da su yadda za su kashe ƙwayoyin cuta na kansa ya yi tasiri wajen magance wani irin cutar sankarar jini.
Kanye West ya shiga cikin wani Pro-Trump Diatribe, yana sanye da MAGA Hat, Bayan SNL bayyanarsa.
Ba a Yi Nasara ba
An yi wa Kanye West ihu a cikin dakin wasan kwaikwayo a lokacin wani shirin Saturday Night Live bayan wani wasan kwaikwayo wanda ya yaba wa Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump kuma ya ce zai yi takara a ofishin a shekarar 2020.
Bayan ya yi waƙar sa ta uku a daren, mai suna Ghost Town wanda a ciki yake sanye da hular Make America Great, ya yi ta yi wa 'yan Democrat ba'a kuma ya sake jaddada goyon bayansa ga Trump.
"A lokuta da dama ina magana da fararen fata kuma suna cewa: "Ta yaya za ka so Trump, shi mai wariyar launin fata ne?"
Da a ce ina da damuwa da wariyar launin fata da na bar Amurka tun da dadewa", in ji shi.
SNL ya fara wasan kwaikwayon tare da wasan kwaikwayo tare da Matt Damon wanda tauraron Hollywood ya yi ba'a da shaidar Brett Kavanaugh a gaban Kwamitin Shari'a na Majalisar Dattijai game da zargin da ake yi na cin zarafin mata da Christine Blasey Ford ta yi.
Kodayake ba a watsa shi ba, mai wasan kwaikwayo Chris Rock ya ɗora hotunan rant na West a kan kafofin watsa labarun.
Ba a bayyana ba idan Rock yana ƙoƙarin yin ba'a da West tare da aikawa.
Har ila yau, West ya yi kuka ga masu sauraro cewa ya sami matsala a baya game da kayan aikinsa.
"Suna matsa mini a bayan fage.
Suka ce, 'kada ka fita a wurin da wannan hat.'
Sun yi mini zagi!
Kuma sai suka ce ina cikin wani wuri sunken, "ya ce, bisa ga Washington Examiner.
West ya ci gaba: "Kuna son ganin wurin da ya nutse?" yana cewa zai "sa mayafin Superman na, saboda wannan yana nufin ba za ku iya gaya mani abin da zan yi ba.
Ka gwada ƙauna".
Bayanansa sun jawo ihu aƙalla sau biyu daga masu sauraro kuma SNL 'yan wasan sun kasance kamar sun ji kunya, Variety ya ruwaito, tare da wani mutum a wurin yana gaya wa littafin: "Dukkan ɗakin ya yi shiru".
An kawo West a matsayin mai maye gurbin marigayi ga mawaƙa Ariana Grande, wanda tsohon saurayinta, mai rairayi Mac Miller ya mutu 'yan kwanaki da suka gabata.
West ya rikitar da mutane da yawa tare da yin waƙar I Love it, sanye da kwalban Perrier.
West ya sami goyon baya daga shugaban kungiyar masu ra'ayin mazan jiya ta TPUSA, Candace Turner wanda ya wallafa a shafinsa na Twitter cewa: "Ga daya daga cikin masu karfin zuciya: Godiya ga tsayawa kan 'yan bindiga".
Amma mai gabatar da shirin tattaunawa Karen Hunter ta tweet cewa West kawai "yana kasancewa wanda yake kuma hakan yana da kyau kwarai da gaske".
"Amma na zabi BA don ba da lada ga wani (ta hanyar sayen kiɗa ko tufafinsa ko tallafawa "fasaharsa") wanda na yi imanin yana rungumar da kuma zubar da akidar da ke cutar da al'ummata.
Yana da 'yanci.
Mu ma haka muke", ta kara da cewa.
Kafin wasan kwaikwayon, rapper ya sanar a Twitter cewa ya canza sunansa, yana cewa yanzu "a hukumance ana kiransa Kanye West".
Ba shi ne na farko mai zane-zane da ya canza sunansu ba kuma ya bi sahun Diddy, wanda aka fi sani da Puff Daddy, Puffy da P Diddy.
Abokin rapper, Snoop Dogg yana da sunan Snoop Lion kuma ba shakka marigayi almara na kiɗa Prince, ya canza sunansa zuwa alama sannan kuma mai zane wanda a baya aka sani da Prince.
Zargin yunkurin kisan kai a gidan cin abinci na Belfast
