Tauraruwar wasan sarauta Kit Harington ta buga a cikin magungunan magunguna
Kit Harington ya shahara saboda rawar da yake yi na takobi a matsayin Jon Snow a cikin HBO na wasan kwaikwayo na tsakar da ke da tashin hankali na tsakiya Game of Thrones.
Amma dan wasan, mai shekaru 31, ya yi tir da ra'ayin jarumin macho, yana cewa irin wannan rawar a kan allo yana nufin samari maza suna jin cewa dole ne su kasance masu tsauri don a girmama su.
Da yake magana da The Sunday Times Al'adu, Kit ya ce ya yi imanin cewa 'wani abu ya yi kuskure' kuma ya yi tambaya kan yadda za a magance matsalar cutar da maza a zamanin #MeToo.
Kit, wanda kwanan nan ya auri 'yar wasan sa na Game of Thrones Rose Leslie, shima mai shekaru 31, ya yarda cewa yana jin 'da karfi' game da magance lamarin.
'Ni kaina ina jin, da karfi, a halin yanzu - a ina muka yi kuskure game da namiji?,' in ji shi.
'Me muka koya wa maza sa'ad da suke girma, game da matsalar da muke gani yanzu?'
Kit ya yi imanin cewa talabijin na iya zama wani bangare na da alhakin hauhawar cutar da maza saboda godiya ga halayenta na maza.
Ya ci gaba: 'Menene aka haifa kuma menene aka koyar?
Me ake koyarwa a talabijin, da kuma a kan tituna, da ke sa samari su ji cewa dole ne su zama wannan bangaren na zama mutum?
Ina ganin wannan ita ce babbar tambayar zamaninmu, ta yaya za mu canja wannan?
Domin babu shakka akwai wani abu da bai dace ba game da samarin.'
A cikin hirar ya kuma yarda cewa ba zai yi wani wasan kwaikwayo na wasan kwaikwayo ba ko kuma ci gaba lokacin da jerin suka zo ga ƙarshe a bazara mai zuwa, yana cewa an 'yi shi da fagen fama da dawakai'.
Daga watan Nuwamba Kit zai fito a cikin farfadowa na Sam Shepard na Gaskiya na Yamma wanda shine labarin wani mai shirya fim da ɗan'uwansa, wanda shi ne ɓarawo.
A kwanan nan dan wasan ya bayyana cewa yana ganin haduwa da matarsa Rose shine mafi kyawun abin da zai fito daga Game of Thrones.
'Na sadu da matata a wannan wasan kwaikwayon, don haka ta wannan hanyar ya ba ni iyalina na nan gaba, da rayuwata daga nan gaba,' in ji shi.
Rose ta taka leda a matsayin Ygritte, ƙaunar ƙaunar halin Kit Jon Snow, a cikin jerin almara na Emmy da ya lashe lambar yabo.
Ma'aurata sun yi aure a watan Yuni na 2018 a kan dalilin mallakar Leslie a Scotland.
HIV/AIDS: China ta ba da rahoton karuwar kashi 14% na sabbin masu cutar
China ta sanar da karuwar kashi 14% a yawan 'yan kasar da ke rayuwa da cutar kanjamau da Aids.
Fiye da mutane 820,000 ne suka kamu da cutar a kasar, in ji jami'an kiwon lafiya.
An samu sabbin mutane 40,000 da suka kamu da cutar a kwata na biyu na 2018 kadai.
Yawancin sababbin maganganu an watsa su ta hanyar jima'i, wanda ke nuna canji daga baya.
A al'ada, HIV ya yadu da sauri a wasu ɓangarorin China sakamakon ƙarin jini da ya kamu da cutar.
Amma adadin mutanen da ke kamuwa da cutar HIV ta wannan hanyar ya ragu zuwa kusan babu, jami'an kiwon lafiya na kasar Sin sun ce a wani taro a lardin Yunnan.
Ko da yake, shekara shekara, adadin waɗanda suke da HIV da Aids a China ya ƙaru da mutane 100,000.
Cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i wata matsala ce mai mahimmanci a cikin al'ummar LGBT na kasar Sin.
An haramta luwadi a kasar Sin a shekarar 1997, amma ana nuna bambanci ga 'yan luwadi da mata.
Saboda dabi'un da ba a yarda da su ba a kasar, binciken ya kiyasta cewa kashi 70-90% na maza da ke yin jima'i da maza za su yi aure da mata.
Yawancin watsa cututtukan na zuwa ne daga rashin kariya ta jima'i a cikin waɗannan alaƙar.
Tun daga 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin samar wa kowa magani don cutar kanjamau a matsayin wani bangare na kokarin magance matsalar.
Maxine Waters ta musanta bayanan da aka fallasa na 'yan majalisar GOP, ta yi ta' karya 'da' ka'idojin makirci '
Wakilin Amurka Maxine Waters a ranar Asabar ta yi tir da zargin da wani ma'aikacinta ya wallafa bayanan sirri na Sanatocin Amurka 'yan Republican guda uku a shafukan Wikipedia na 'yan majalisar.
Los Angeles Democrat ya tabbatar da cewa da'awar da ake pedal da "ƙananan-dama-reshe" pundits da yanar.
"Ƙarya, ƙarya, da ƙarin ƙazamar ƙarya", Waters ya ce a cikin wata sanarwa a kan Twitter.
Bayanan da aka bayar sun hada da adireshin gida da lambobin waya na Amurka. Lindsey Graham na South Carolina, da Mike Lee da Orrin Hatch, duka na Utah.
Bayanin ya bayyana a yanar gizo a ranar Alhamis, wanda wani ba a san shi ba ya sanya shi a Capitol Hill yayin sauraron kwamitin Majalisar Dattawa kan zargin cin zarafin jima'i da aka yi wa dan takarar Kotun Koli Brett Kavanaugh.
Bayanan sun zo ne bayan sanatocin uku sun yi wa Kavanaugh tambayoyi.
Shafukan masu ra'ayin mazan jiya kamar su Gateway Pundit da RedState sun ba da rahoton cewa adireshin IP wanda ke gano asalin sakonnin yana da alaƙa da ofishin Waters kuma ya ba da bayanan wani memba na ma'aikatan Waters, Hill ya ruwaito.
"Wannan zargi mara tushe gaba daya karya ne kuma karya ne kwata-kwata", Waters ya ci gaba.
"Wanda ke cikin ma'aikatana - wanda aka yi wa asirinsa, bayanansa, da kuma tsaro sakamakon wadannan maganganu na zamba da karya - ba shi da alhakin wannan bayanan.
Wannan zargi marar tushe ƙarya ce ƙwarai".
Sanarwar Waters da sauri ta jawo suka a kan layi, gami da tsohon sakataren watsa labarai na Fadar White House Ari Fleischer.
"Wannan musun yana da fushi", in ji Fleischer.
"Wannan ya nuna cewa ba ta da halin zama memba na Majalisa.
Idan aka zargi wani da wani abu da bai yi ba, bai kamata ya yi fushi ba.
Kada su yi tawaye.
Bai kamata su yi shakkar dalilin wanda yake tuhumarsu ba.
Dole ne su kasance masu nutsuwa da kwanciyar hankali".
