Akwai abubuwa guda biyu masu kyau a wannan sabon fitowar JE.
Na so Johnny English yana kusantar helikafta yayin da yake sanye da kayan yakin na tsakiyar zamanai kuma ruwan tabarau na rotor na ɗan lokaci suna ta da kwalkwali.
Kyautar Atkinson don wasan kwaikwayo na jiki yana kan nuni, amma abin dariya yana jin daɗi sosai kuma ba shi da kyau, musamman kamar yadda alamun fina-finai masu "tauri" kamar 007 da kuma Ofishin Jakadancin da kansu yanzu suna ba da tabbaci da abin dariya a matsayin kayan abinci.
Abin dariya yana jin kamar an jefa shi ga yara maimakon manya, kuma a gare ni Johnny English 's wacky misadventures ba su da kwarewa da kuma mayar da hankali kamar Atkinson's silent-movie gags a cikin persona na Bean.
Babban abin da ke faruwa yanzu shi ne cewa Birtaniya tana cikin matsala mai tsanani.
