Masu ba ta shawara a fannin leken asiri sun sanar da ita cewa tun da aka yi wa kowane ɗan leƙen asiri da ke aiki, za ta fitar da wani daga cikin waɗanda suka yi ritaya.
Kuma wannan yana nufin ba da kunya ga Johnny English kansa, yanzu yana aiki a matsayin malamin makaranta a wani wuri mai kyau, amma yana ba da darussan ba da labari ba yadda za a kasance mai aiki a asirce: wasu kyawawan barkwanci a nan, kamar yadda Turanci ke ba da makarantar Rock-type na leken asiri.
