A halin yanzu, Firaministan yana fadawa cikin haɗari a ƙarƙashin sihirin biliyan mai fasaha mai ban sha'awa wanda ke da'awar cewa zai iya magance matsalolin kwamfutar Birtaniya: Jason Volta mai ban mamaki, wanda Jake Lacy ya buga.
Turanci da Bough sun fara odyssey na high-jinks masu ban dariya: sun ɓoye a matsayin masu jiran aiki, sun ba da wuta a gidan abinci na Faransa mai haske; sun haifar da rikici da suka yi ta hanyar shiga jirgin ruwan Volta; kuma Ingilishi ya haifar da rashin tsari yayin da yake ƙoƙarin amfani da na'urar kai ta Virtual Reality don sanin kansa da cikin gidan Volta.
