Labour ta musanta cewa tana tsara wani shiri na 'yan Burtaniya don yin aiki kwana hudu a mako amma a biya su kwana biyar
Jam'iyyar Labour ta Jeremy Corbyn za ta yi la'akari da wani tsari mai zurfi wanda zai ga 'yan Birtaniya suna aiki kwanaki hudu a mako - amma ana biyan su biyar.
Jam'iyyar ta ce tana son shugabannin kamfanin su ba da kuɗin da aka samu ta hanyar juyin juya halin fasaha (AI) ga ma'aikata ta hanyar ba su ƙarin hutu.
Zai ga ma'aikata suna jin daɗin ƙarshen mako na kwana uku - amma har yanzu suna ɗaukar kuɗin gida ɗaya.
Majiyoyi sun ce ra'ayin zai "dace" da tsarin tattalin arzikin jam'iyyar da kuma shirin karkatar da kasar don tallafawa ma'aikata.
Canja zuwa kwana hudu a mako an amince da shi ta hanyar Majalisa ta Unionungiyar Unionungiya a matsayin hanya ga ma'aikata don cin gajiyar canjin tattalin arziki.
Wani babban jami'in jam'iyyar Labour ya gaya wa Sunday Times: "Ana sa ran za a sanar da sake nazarin manufofin kafin karshen shekara.
'Ba zai faru ba dare da rana amma aikin kwana hudu a mako shine burin da ya dace da tsarin jam'iyyar don daidaita tattalin arziki a cikin ma'aikata da kuma tsarin dabarun masana'antu na jam'iyyar.'
Jam'iyyar Labour ba za ta kasance ta farko ba don tallafawa irin wannan ra'ayin, tare da Green Party da ke yin alkawarin aiki na kwana hudu a lokacin yakin neman zaben zaben 2017.
A halin yanzu, duk da haka, ba a yarda da burin da Labour Party a matsayin duka ba.
Wani mai magana da yawun jam'iyyar Labour ya ce: 'Kwana hudu na aiki ba siyasa ba ce ta jam'iyyar kuma jam'iyyar ba ta yin la'akari da hakan.'
Shadow Chancellor John McDonnell yayi amfani da taron ma'aikatar ma'aikata na makon da ya gabata don bayyana hangen nesan sa na juyin juya halin gurguzu a cikin tattalin arziki.
Mista McDonnell ya ce ya kuduri aniyar dawo da iko daga 'shugabannin da ba su da fuska' da kuma 'masu riba' a kamfanonin amfani.
