Menene Bikin 'Yan Kasa na Duniya kuma Shin Ya Yi Wani Abu don Rage Talauci?
A wannan Asabar New York za ta karbi bakuncin bikin 'yan kasa na duniya, wani taron kiɗa na shekara-shekara wanda ke da jerin taurari masu ban sha'awa da ke yin wasan kwaikwayo da kuma irin wannan manufa mai ban sha'awa; kawo karshen talauci a duniya.
Yanzu a shekara ta bakwai, bikin Global Citizen zai ga dubun dubatan mutane sun yi tururuwa zuwa Babban Lawn na Central Park don ba kawai jin daɗin ayyukan kamar Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes ba, har ma don wayar da kan jama'a game da ainihin burin taron na kawo ƙarshen matsanancin talauci zuwa 2030.
Bikin 'Yan Kasa na Duniya, wanda ya bayyana a shekarar 2012, ya kasance wani ci gaba ne na Tsarin Talauci na Duniya, wata kungiyar bayar da shawarwari ta duniya da ke fatan kawo karshen talauci ta hanyar kara yawan mutanen da ke gwagwarmayar da ita.
Don karɓar tikiti kyauta don taron (sai dai idan kun kasance a shirye ku biya kuɗin tikitin VIP), masu halartar wasan kwaikwayo dole ne su kammala jerin ayyuka, ko "ayyuka" irin su ba da kai, imel ɗin shugaban duniya, yin kira ta waya ko kuma duk wasu hanyoyi masu ma'ana don taimakawa wajen wayar da kan jama'a game da burin su na kawar da talauci.
Amma yaya nasarar Global Citizen ta kasance da shekaru 12 da suka rage don cimma burinta?
Shin ra'ayin saka wa mutane kyauta tare da wasan kwaikwayo kyauta hanya ce ta gaske don shawo kan mutane su buƙaci kira don aiki, ko kuma kawai wani yanayin da ake kira "clicktivism" - mutane suna jin kamar suna yin canji na gaske ta hanyar sanya hannu kan takardar neman izini ta yanar gizo ko aikawa da tweet?
Tun daga 2011, Global Citizen ta ce ta yi rikodin "ayyuka" sama da miliyan 19 daga magoya bayanta, suna turawa zuwa ga wasu manufofi daban-daban.
Ya ce wadannan ayyukan sun taimaka wa shugabannin duniya su sanar da alkawurra da manufofi da suka kai dala biliyan 37 wanda aka saita don shafar rayuwar mutane sama da biliyan 2.25 nan da 2030.
A farkon 2018, kungiyar ta ambaci alkawura da sanarwar 390 da suka samo asali daga ayyukanta, aƙalla dala biliyan 10 daga cikinsu an riga an biya ko tara kuɗi.
Kungiyar ta kiyasta cewa kudaden da aka samu ya zuwa yanzu sun yi tasiri kai tsaye ga kusan mutane miliyan 649 a duk duniya.
Wasu daga cikin mahimman alkawurran sun hada da The Power of Nutrition, haɗin gwiwar masu saka jari da masu aiwatarwa na Burtaniya da ke da alhakin "taimaka wa yara su girma zuwa cikakkiyar damar su", suna yin alƙawarin samar da Ruwanda da dala miliyan 35 don taimakawa wajen kawo ƙarshen rashin abinci mai gina jiki a cikin gundumar bayan karɓar tweets sama da 4,700 daga Global Citizens.
"Tare da goyon bayan gwamnatin Burtaniya, masu ba da tallafi, gwamnatocin ƙasa, da Global Citizens kamar ku, za mu iya sanya rashin adalci na rashin abinci mai gina jiki a cikin tarihin", in ji jakadan The Power of Nutrition Tracey Ullman ya gaya wa taron a yayin wani wasan kwaikwayo a London a watan Afrilu 2018.
Kungiyar ta kuma ce bayan da aka dauki matakan da suka fi na 5,000 a kan Burtaniya don inganta abinci mai gina jiki ga uwaye da yara, gwamnati ta sanar da tallafin kudi ga wani aiki, The Power of Nutrition, wanda zai kai ga mata da yara miliyan 5 tare da ayyukan abinci mai gina jiki.
A cikin amsar daya daga cikin tambayoyin da aka yi a shafin yanar gizon da ke tambaya "me ya sa kuke tunanin za mu iya kawo karshen talauci?"
Global citizen ya amsa: "Zai zama hanya mai tsawo da wahala - wani lokacin za mu faɗi kuma mu kasa.
Amma, kamar manyan 'yancin jama'a da kuma anti-apartheid ƙungiyoyi kafin mu, za mu yi nasara, domin mu ne mafi iko tare.
Janet Jackson, da Weeknd, Shawn Mendes, Cardi B, Janelle Monáe suna daga cikin wasu ayyukan da ke gudana a taron na wannan shekara a New York, wanda Deborra-Lee Furness da Hugh Jackman za su shirya.
Amurka na iya amfani da Sojan Ruwa don "kunkar" don hana fitar da makamashin Rasha - Sakataren Cikin Gida
Washington na iya "in ya zama dole" ya yi amfani da sojan ruwanta don hana makamashin Rasha shiga kasuwanni, ciki har da Gabas ta Tsakiya, Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida na Amurka Ryan Zinke ya bayyana, kamar yadda Washington Examiner ya nakalto.
Zinke ya yi zargin cewa shigar da Rasha a Siriya - musamman, inda take aiki a gayyatar halattacciyar gwamnati - hujja ce ta bincika sabbin kasuwannin makamashi.
