Jihohi 18, DC sun goyi bayan kalubalantar sabuwar manufofin neman mafaka
Jihohi goma sha takwas da District of Columbia suna tallafawa kalubalanci doka ga sabuwar manufar Amurka da ke hana mafaka ga wadanda ke tserewa daga ƙungiyoyin 'yan bindiga ko tashin hankali na gida.
Wakilan jihohi 18 da gundumar sun gabatar da takardar abokantaka a ranar Juma'a a Washington don tallafawa mai neman mafaka wanda ke kalubalantar manufar, NBC News ta ruwaito.
Cikakken sunan mai karar a cikin shari'ar Grace v. Sessions da Unionungiyar 'Yancin Jama'ar Amurka ta gabatar a watan Agusta kan manufofin tarayya ba a bayyana ba.
Ta ce abokin aikinta "da 'ya'yansa' yan kungiyar 'yan ta'adda masu ta'adda, " sun wulakanta ta amma jami'an Amurka sun ki amincewa da bukatar ta neman mafaka a ranar 20 ga Yuli.
An tsare ta a Texas.
Lauyoyin jihohi da ke goyon bayan Grace sun bayyana El Salvador, Honduras da Guatemala, wadanda ke samar da dimbin masu neman mafaka a Amurka, a matsayin kasashe da ke fuskantar matsalolin da ke fama da ƙungiyoyi da kuma tashin hankali na gida.
Sabuwar manufar mafaka ta Amurka ta sake yanke hukuncin 2014 ta Hukumar daukaka kara ta Baƙi wanda ya ba da damar baƙi ba tare da izini ba da ke tserewa daga tashin hankali na gida don neman mafaka.
Babban Lauyan gundumar Columbia Karl Racine ya ce a cikin wata sanarwa a ranar Juma'a cewa sabuwar manufar "ta yi watsi da shekarun da suka gabata na jihar, tarayya, da kuma dokokin kasa da kasa".
