Jakadan Amurka ya zargi China da 'ta'addanci' tare da 'tallace-tallacen farfaganda'
Mako guda bayan wata jaridar kasar China ta buga wani shafi na hudu a cikin wata jaridar Amurka da ke nuna amfanin da ke tattare da cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China, jakadan Amurka a China ya zargi Beijing da yin amfani da jaridun Amurka don yada farfaganda.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump a ranar Laraba da ta gabata ya yi magana game da karin kudin da China Daily ta biya a cikin Des Moines Register - jaridar da ta fi yawan sayarwa a jihar Iowa - bayan da ta zargi China da neman tsoma baki a zaben majalisun Amurka na ranar 6 ga Nuwamba, zargin da China ta musanta.
Zargin da Trump ya yi na cewa Beijing na kokarin tsoma baki a zaben Amurka ya nuna cewa jami'an Amurka sun shaida wa Reuters cewa wani sabon mataki ne na yakin da Washington ke yi na matsa lamba ga China.
Duk da yake al'ada ce ga gwamnatocin kasashen waje su sanya tallace-tallace don inganta cinikayya, Beijing da Washington a halin yanzu suna cikin rikici na cinikayya wanda ya ga sun daidaita matakan da aka yi a kan juna.
Farashin da China ta dauka a farkon yakin cinikayya an tsara shi ne don buga masu fitarwa a jihohi kamar Iowa wadanda suka goyi bayan Jam'iyyar Republican ta Trump, masana na China da Amurka sun ce.
Terry Branstad, jakadan Amurka a China kuma tsohon gwamnan Iowa na dogon lokaci, babban mai fitar da kayayyakin gona zuwa China, ya ce Beijing ya cutar da ma'aikatan Amurka, manoma da 'yan kasuwa.
China, Branstad ya rubuta a cikin wani ra'ayi a cikin Des Moines Register na ranar Lahadi, "yanzu yana ninka wannan zalunci ta hanyar gudanar da tallan farfaganda a cikin 'yan jaridarmu".
"A cikin yada farfagandar, gwamnatin kasar Sin tana amfani da al'adun Amurka na 'yancin faɗar albarkacin baki da' yancin 'yan jarida ta hanyar sanya tallan da aka biya a cikin Des Moines Register", in ji Branstad.
"A akasin wannan, a gidan jaridu a kan titi a nan Beijing, za ku sami 'yan muryoyi masu banbanci kuma ba za ku ga wani abin da ya dace ba game da ra'ayoyin da jama'ar kasar Sin ke da shi game da yanayin tattalin arzikin kasar Sin, saboda cewa kafofin watsa labarai suna karkashin ikon jam'iyyar kwaminisanci ta kasar Sin, " in ji shi.
Ya kara da cewa "daya daga cikin fitattun jaridun kasar Sin ta kauce wa tayin da aka yi mata na buga" labarinta, ko da yake bai ce wace jarida ba.
'Yan Republican suna gujewa mata masu jefa kuri'a a gaban zaben tsakiyar lokaci tare da Kavanaugh, masu sharhi sun yi gargadin
Yayin da manyan 'yan Republican ke jiran kare dan takarar Kotun Koli Brett Kavanaugh a kan zarginsa da ake yi na cin zarafin mata, manazarta sun yi gargadin za su ga koma baya, musamman daga mata, a lokacin zaben tsakiyar wa'adi mai zuwa.
Abubuwan da ke kewaye da wannan sun kasance masu girma, kuma yawancin 'yan Republican sun riga sun nuna cewa suna so su ci gaba da yin zabe.
Waɗannan abubuwan ba za a iya dawo da su ba, " Grant Reeher, farfesa a fannin kimiyyar siyasa a Makarantar Maxwell na Jami'ar Syracuse ya gaya wa The Hill don labarin da aka buga a ranar Asabar.
Reeher ya ce yana shakkar cewa Sanata Jeff Flake (R-Arizona) na karshe na FBI na bincike zai isa ya kwantar da masu jefa kuri'a.
"Mata ba za su manta da abin da ya faru jiya ba - ba za su manta da shi gobe ba kuma ba a watan Nuwamba ba", in ji Karine Jean-Pierre, babban mai ba da shawara da kuma mai magana da yawun kungiyar MoveOn a ranar Juma'a, a cewar jaridar Washington, DC.
A safiyar Juma'a, masu zanga-zangar sun yi taken "Nuwamba yana zuwa!" kamar yadda suka nuna a cikin farfajiyar Majalisar Dattawa yayin da 'yan Republican da ke kula da Kwamitin Shari'a suka zaɓi ci gaba da zaɓaɓɓen Kavanaugh duk da shaidar Dr. Christine Blasey Ford, Mic ya ruwaito.
"Kulawar dimokiradiyya da motsawa za su kasance daga jadawalin", Stu Rothenberg, mai nazarin siyasa na siyasa, ya gaya wa shafin labarai.
"Mutane suna cewa ya riga ya yi yawa; hakan gaskiya ne.
Amma zai iya zama mafi girma, musamman a tsakanin masu jefa kuri'a na mata masu juyawa a cikin unguwannin da kuma masu jefa kuri'a matasa, masu shekaru 18 zuwa 29, waɗanda yayin da ba sa son shugaban, sau da yawa ba sa jefa kuri'a. "
Tun kafin shaidar da Ford ta bayar a bainar jama'a ta bayyana zarginta na cin zarafin mata da aka yi wa dan takarar Kotun Koli, manazarta sun nuna cewa za a iya samun koma baya idan 'yan Republican suka ci gaba da tabbatar da shi.
"Wannan ya zama rikici ga GOP", in ji Michael Steele, tsohon shugaban kwamitin Republican National, a farkon makon da ya gabata, a cewar NBC News.
"Ba batun kuri'ar kwamitin bane ko kuri'ar karshe ko kuma an sanya Kavanaugh a benci, ya kuma shafi yadda 'yan Republican suka magance wannan da kuma yadda suka bi da ita", Guy Cecil, darektan Priorities USA, wata kungiya da ke taimakawa wajen zabar' yan Democrat, ya nuna wa tashar labarai.
Koyaya, Amurkawa sun bayyana sun ɗan rarrabu kan wanda za su yarda da shi bayan shaidar Ford da Kavanaugh, tare da ɗan ƙara kasancewa tare da na biyun.
Wani sabon binciken da aka gudanar daga YouGov ya nuna cewa kashi 41 cikin dari na masu amsawa sun yarda ko kuma sun gaskata shaidar Ford, yayin da kashi 35 cikin dari suka ce tabbas ko kuma sun yarda da Kavanaugh.
Bugu da kari, kashi 38 suka ce sun yi tunanin Kavanaugh ya yi karya a lokacin da yake shaidar, yayin da kashi 30 suka ce haka ne game da Ford.
Bayan turawa daga Flake, FBI a halin yanzu tana binciken zargin da Ford ya gabatar da kuma aƙalla wani mai tuhuma, Deborah Ramirez, The Guardian ya ruwaito.
Ford ta shaida a gaban kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattawa a karkashin rantsuwar da ta yi a makon da ya gabata cewa Kavanaugh ya yi mata fyade a lokacin da yake da shekara 17.
Ramirez ya yi zargin cewa wanda aka zaba a kotun koli ya nuna mata al'aurarsa yayin da suka halarci wani biki a lokacin da suke karatu a Yale a cikin shekarun 1980.
Mai Kirkirar Duniyar Yanar Gizo na Duniya Yana Shirin Kafa Sabuwar Intanet da Zai Yi Nasara da Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo, yana kaddamar da wani kamfani wanda yake son ya yi gasa da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Labarin fasahar fasahar fasahar zamani, Inrupt, kamfani ne wanda ya gina daga Berners-Lee's Open Source dandamali Solid.
Solid yana bawa masu amfani damar zaɓar inda aka adana bayanan su da kuma waɗanne mutane aka ba su damar samun waɗanne bayanai.
A cikin wata hira ta musamman da Kamfanin Kamfanin, Berners-Lee ya yi ba'a cewa manufar Inrupt ita ce " mamaye duniya. "
"Dole ne mu yi shi yanzu", in ji shi game da farawa.
"Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi".
Aikace-aikacen yana amfani da fasahar Solid don bawa mutane damar ƙirƙirar "kayan ajiyar bayanan kan layi na sirri" ko POD.
Yana iya ƙunsar jerin lambobi, jerin abubuwan da za a yi, kalanda, ɗakin ɗakin kiɗa da sauran kayan aiki na sirri da na sana'a.
Yana da kamar Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify duk samuwa a kan daya browser da kuma duk a lokaci guda.
Abinda ke da ban mamaki game da bayanan sirri na kan layi shine cewa ya dogara ne akan mai amfani wanda zai iya samun damar irin wannan bayanin.
Kamfanin ya kira shi "karfafawa ta hanyar bayanai".
Manufar Inrupt, a cewar Shugaba John Bruce, shine kamfanin ya kawo albarkatu, tsari da ƙwarewar da ta dace don taimakawa samar da Solid ga kowa.
Kamfanin a halin yanzu ya ƙunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, wani dandamali na tsaro da IBM ya saya, wasu masu haɓaka ma'aikata da aka ƙulla su yi aiki a kan aikin, da kuma al'ummar masu ba da agaji.
Farawa wannan makon, masu haɓaka fasaha a duk faɗin duniya na iya ƙirƙirar aikace-aikacen su na rarrabawa ta amfani da kayan aikin da ake samu akan gidan yanar gizon Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa ba sa magana da "Facebook da Google game da ko gabatar da cikakken canji inda duk tsarin kasuwancin su ya lalace gaba daya cikin dare.
"Ba mu nemi izinin su ba".
A cikin wani rubutu a kan Medium da aka buga a ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa Inrupt "aikinta shi ne samar da makamashi na kasuwanci da kuma yanayin halittu don taimakawa kare mutunci da ingancin sabon gidan yanar gizo da aka gina a kan Solid".
A shekara ta 1994, Berners-Lee ya canja hanyar sadarwa ta Intanet sa'ad da ya kafa rukunin yanar gizo mai suna World Wide Web Consortium a Massachusetts Institute of Technology.
A cikin 'yan watannin nan, Berners-Lee ya kasance mai rinjaye a cikin muhawarar tsaka tsaki na yanar gizo.
Ko da yayin ƙaddamar da Inrupt, Berners-Lee zai kasance wanda ya kafa kuma Daraktan World Wide Web Consortium, Gidauniyar Gida da Cibiyar Bayanai ta Bude.
"Ina da kyakkyawan fata ga wannan zamani na gaba na yanar gizo", in ji Berners-Lee.
