An sake jinkirta sabon jirgin yakin Jamus
Ya kamata a fara amfani da sabon jirgin ruwan na Sojojin Ruwa na Jamus a shekarar 2014 don maye gurbin tsofaffin jiragen ruwan yakin Cold War, amma ba zai kasance a wurin ba har zuwa aƙalla shekara mai zuwa saboda tsarin da ba daidai ba da kuma tsadar kuɗi, kafofin watsa labarai na gida sun ruwaito.
An dage aikin "Rheinland-Pfalz", babban jirgin ruwan sabon nau'in Baden-Wuerttemberg-class frigates, har zuwa farkon rabin shekarar 2019, a cewar jaridar Die Zeit da ke ambaton wani mai magana da yawun sojoji.
Da jirgin ya kamata ya shiga cikin Sojojin Ruwa a cikin 2014, amma matsalolin da ke damuwa bayan bayarwa sun shafi makomar wannan babban aikin.
Jirgin ruwa guda hudu na Baden-Wuerttemberg wanda Navy ya umarci baya a 2007 zai zo ne a matsayin maye gurbin tsofaffin jiragen ruwa na Bremen.
An fahimci cewa za su nuna wani m bindiga, wani tsararru na anti-jirgin sama da kuma anti-jirgin makamai masu linzami da kuma wasu stealth fasahar, kamar rage radar, infrared da kuma acoustic sa hannu.
Sauran mahimman abubuwa sun haɗa da tsawan lokacin kulawa - ya kamata ya yiwu a tura sabbin jiragen ruwa na zamani har zuwa shekaru biyu daga tashar jiragen ruwa.
Amma, Die Zeit ta lura cewa, jinkirin da ake yi a kai a kai yana nufin cewa jiragen yaƙin zamani da aka ce suna ba Jamus damar nuna ikonta a ƙasashen waje, za su zama tsofaffi kafin a soma amfani da su.
Jirgin ruwan F125 da ba shi da kyau ya yi kanun labarai a bara, lokacin da Sojojin Ruwa na Jamus suka ki amincewa da aiki da jirgin kuma suka mayar da shi zuwa tashar jirgin ruwa ta Blohm & Voss a Hamburg.
Wannan shi ne karo na farko da Sojojin Ruwa suka mayar da jirgin zuwa mai gina jirgin bayan bayarwa.
An san kadan game da dalilan da ke bayan dawowar, amma kafofin watsa labarai na Jamus sun ambaci wasu mahimman "kurakurai na software da kayan aiki" waɗanda suka sa jirgin ya zama mara amfani idan aka tura shi aikin yaƙi.
Rashin rashin software yana da mahimmanci musamman kamar yadda jiragen ruwa na Baden-Wuerttemberg za su yi aiki da ma'aikatan jirgin ruwa na kimanin 120 - kawai rabin ma'aikatan jirgin sama na tsofaffi na Bremen.
Hakanan, ya bayyana cewa jirgin yana da nauyi sosai wanda ke rage aikinsa kuma yana iyakance ikon Navy na ƙara haɓakawa a nan gaba.
Ana tsammanin "Rheinland-Pfalz" mai nauyin tan 7,000 ya ninka sau biyu na jiragen ruwa masu kama da irin wadanda Jamusawa suka yi amfani da su a yakin duniya na biyu.
Baya ga kayan aikin da ba su da kyau, farashin aikin gaba ɗaya - haɗe da horar da ma'aikatan jirgin - yana zama matsala.
An ce ya kai € 3.1billion ($ 3.6bn) - sama daga farkon € 2.2billion.
Matsalolin da ke damun sabbin jiragen ruwa sun zama masu mahimmanci musamman dangane da gargadin da aka yi kwanan nan cewa ƙarfin jirgin ruwan Jamus yana raguwa.
A farkon wannan shekarar, Hans-Peter Bartels, shugaban kwamitin tsaro na majalisar dokokin Jamus, ya yarda cewa Rundunar Sojan Ruwa a zahiri "ta kasa samun jiragen ruwa da za a iya turawa".
Jami'in ya ce batun ya yi ta da yawa a tsawon lokaci, saboda an cire tsoffin jiragen ruwa amma ba a samar da sabbin jiragen ruwa ba.
Ya yi nadama cewa babu wani daga cikin jirgin ruwa na Baden-Wuerttemberg-class da zai iya shiga Navy.
