Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu sakamakon girgizar kasa da tsunami da suka afkawa birnin Palu na kasar Indonesia ranar Juma'a, in ji jami'ai, tare da sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu.
Tare da katsewar sadarwa, jami'an agaji ba su sami damar samun wani bayani daga Donggala regency, wani yanki a arewacin Palu wanda ya fi kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasa mai girman 7.5.
A Palu, an kwashe mutane sama da 16,000 bayan bala'in ya auku.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palu da Donggala, a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu babban birni ne na lardin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya, wanda ke a ƙarshen ƙanƙantar bay a gabar yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, wanda ke da kimanin mutane 379,800 a shekarar 2017.
Birnin yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da kafuwa lokacin da girgizar kasa da tsunami suka faru.
Donggala yanki ne mai mulkin mallaka wanda ya kai fiye da kilomita 300 na gabar teku a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi .
Gundumar, yanki ne na gudanarwa a ƙarƙashin lardi, yana da kimanin mutane 299,200 a cikin 2017.
Kifi da noma sune manyan abubuwan da ke da alhakin tattalin arzikin lardin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya, musamman yankin Donggala na gabar teku.
Har ila yau, hakar ma'adinai na nickel yana da mahimmanci a lardin, amma galibi ana mai da hankali ne a cikin Morowali, a gabar da ke gaban Sulawesi.
Palu da Donggala sun sha fama da tsunami sau da yawa a cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata, a cewar Hukumar Kula da Bala'o'i ta Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, guguwar tsunami ta kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ta lalata ɗaruruwan gidaje a Donggala.
Tsunami ya kuma kai yammacin Donggala a 1996, inda ya kashe tara.
Indonesia tana zaune a kan Zoben Wutar Pacific mai girgizar ƙasa kuma ana yawan girgizar ƙasa a kai a kai.
Ga wasu daga cikin manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da aka yi a shekarun baya bayan nan:
2004: Babban girgizar ƙasa a yammacin gabar lardin Aceh na Indonesia a arewacin Sumatra a ranar 26 ga Disamba ya haifar da tsunami wanda ya buge kasashe 14, ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su a Aceh.
2005: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afka wa gabar yammacin Sumatra a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias, kusa da gaɓar Sumatra.
2006: Wani girgizar kasa mai girman 6.8 ya afka kudu da Java, tsibirin da ya fi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, ya haifar da tsunami da ya yi karo da gabar kudancin kasar, ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Girgizar ƙasa mai girman 7.6 ta afka kusa da garin Padang, babban birnin lardin Sumatra ta Yamma.
An kashe mutane fiye da 1,100.
2010: Girgizar kasa mai girman 7.5 ta afku a daya daga cikin tsibirin Mentawai, daga Sumatra, wanda ya haifar da tsunami mai tsawon mita 10 wanda ya lalata ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane kusan 300.
2016: Girgizar kasa ta afkawa yankin Pidie Jaya a Aceh, ta haifar da lalacewa da fargaba yayin da mutane suka tuna da lalacewar mummunar girgizar kasa da tsunami na 2004.
Babu tsunami da aka jawo a wannan karon, amma fiye da 100 aka kashe ta rushewar gine-gine.
2018: Manyan girgizar kasa ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok na Indonesia, inda ta kashe mutane sama da 500, galibi a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma ta bar dubban masu yawon bude ido sun makale na ɗan lokaci.
