Girgizar kasa da tsunami a Indonesia: daruruwan mutane sun mutu
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu bayan girgizar kasa ta afkawa tsibirin Sulawesi na Indonesia a ranar Juma'a.
Girgizar kasa mai girman maki 7.5 ta haifar da tsunami kuma ta lalata dubban gidaje.
Wutar lantarki da hanyoyin sadarwa sun ragu tare da tsammanin mutuwar da ake tsammanin zai karu a cikin kwanaki masu zuwa.
Girgizar ta auku ne a tsakiyar Sulawesi wanda ke arewa maso gabashin babban birnin Indonesia, Jakarta.
Ana ta yawo da bidiyo a shafukan sada zumunta da ke nuna lokacin da abin ya faru.
Daruruwan mutane sun taru don bikin rairayin bakin teku a birnin Palu lokacin da tsunami ya buga a bakin teku.
Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya suna neman hukuncin kisa na musamman ga wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci na NYC
Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya a New York suna neman hukuncin kisa ga Sayfullo Saipov, wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci na New York City wanda ya kashe mutane takwas - wani hukunci ne da ba a taba aiwatar da shi ba a jihar don aikata laifuka na tarayya tun 1953.
Saipov, mai shekaru 30, an yi zargin ya yi amfani da motar haya ta gida don aiwatar da hari a kan hanyar keke a kan titin West Side Highway a Lower Manhattan, yana yanka masu tafiya da keke a hanyarsa a ranar Oct.
Domin tabbatar da hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara za su tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya kashe mutane takwas da gangan kuma ya yi "aikin ganganci" ya yi musu mummunar rauni, a cewar sanarwar da aka yi na neman hukuncin kisa, wanda aka shigar a Kudancin New York.
Dukkanin waɗannan laifuka suna ɗaukar hukuncin kisa, bisa ga takardar kotu.
Makonni bayan harin, babban kotun tarayya ta tuhumi Saipov da tuhumar da ta kunshi tuhuma 22 da suka hada da tuhumar kisa takwas da ake amfani da ita wajen taimakawa masu satar kudi, wanda masu gabatar da kara na tarayya ke amfani da shi a shari'o'in aikata laifuka, da kuma tuhumar tashin hankali da lalata motoci.
Harin ya buƙaci "tsara mai mahimmanci da kuma shiri", in ji masu gabatar da kara, suna bayyana yadda Saipov ya aiwatar da shi a matsayin "mai banƙyama, zalunci da lalata".
"Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya haifar da rauni, lalacewa, da asara ga iyalai da abokai na Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza, da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco, "in ji sanarwar niyyar.
Biyar daga cikin wadanda suka mutu 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga Argentina.
Shekaru goma kenan da wani al'amari na kisa ya shiga hannun kotun da ke kudancin New York.
Wanda ake tuhuma, Khalid Barnes, an yanke masa hukuncin kisan wasu masu sayar da miyagun kwayoyi biyu amma a karshe an yanke masa hukuncin rai da rai a kurkuku a watan Satumbar 2009.
A karo na karshe da aka zartar da hukuncin kisa a wata shari'ar tarayya ta New York a shekarar 1953 ga Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata da aka kashe bayan da aka yanke musu hukuncin kisa na yin makirci don yin leƙen asiri ga Tarayyar Soviet a lokacin Cold War shekaru biyu da suka gabata.
Dukansu Rosenbergs an kashe su ta wurin kujerar lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
Saipov, dan asalin Uzbekistan, ya nuna rashin nadama a cikin kwanaki da watanni bayan harin, a cewar takardun kotu.
Ya bayyana wa masu bincike cewa yana jin dadi game da abin da ya yi, 'yan sanda sun ce.
Saipov ya gaya wa hukumomi cewa an yi wahayi zuwa gare shi don aiwatar da harin bayan kallon bidiyon ISIS a kan wayarsa, a cewar tuhumar.
Ya kuma nemi a nuna tutar ISIS a cikin ɗakin asibitin sa, in ji 'yan sanda.
Ya yi ikirarin cewa ba shi da laifi a kan tuhumar da ake yi masa.
David Patton, daya daga cikin masu kare jama'a na tarayya da ke wakiltar Saipov, ya ce sun "bayyana sun yi takaici" da hukuncin da ke gaban masu gabatar da kara.
"Muna tunanin shawarar neman hukuncin kisa maimakon karɓar laifin da aka yanke wa rai a kurkuku ba tare da yiwuwar sakin ba zai tsawaita raunin waɗannan abubuwan da suka faru ga duk wanda abin ya shafa", in ji Patton.
Kungiyar kare Saipov a baya ta nemi masu gabatar da kara da kada su nemi hukuncin kisa.
Tory MP ya ce ya kamata a sanya Nigel Farage a matsayin wanda zai jagoranci tattaunawar Brexit
Nigel Farage ya sha alwashin 'tara sojojin mutane' a yau a lokacin zanga-zangar a taron Tory.
Tsohon shugaban Ukip ya ce 'yan siyasa dole ne su ji zafin' Eurosceptics - kamar yadda daya daga cikin 'yan majalisa na Theresa May ya ba da shawarar cewa ya kamata ya zama mai kula da tattaunawar da EU.
Dan majalisar na baya-bayan nan mai ra'ayin mazan jiya Peter Bone ya fadawa masu zanga-zanga a Birmingham cewa, Birtaniya 'da ta fita' da yanzu idan Mr Farage ya kasance sakataren Brexit.
Amma kalubalen da Mrs May ke fuskanta wajen sulhunta sahunta mai zurfi ya kara nunawa ta hanyar masu goyon bayan Remain Tories da suka shiga wani zanga-zangar daban da Brexit a cikin birni.
Firayim Minista na fama da ci gaba da shirin sulhunta na Chequers a kan hanya a cikin hare-haren da 'yan Brexit, Remainers da EU ke kaiwa.
'Yan kungiyar Allies sun dage cewa za ta ci gaba da kokarin cimma yarjejeniya da Brussels duk da irin wannan martani - da kuma tilasta wa Eurosceptics da Labour su zabi tsakanin kunshin nata da "hargitsi".
Mista Bone ya gaya wa barin barin barin barin barin barin a Solihull cewa yana so ya 'check Chequers'.
Ya ba da shawarar cewa ya kamata a sanya Mista Farage a matsayin takwaransa kuma a ba shi alhakin tattaunawa da Brussels.
'Da ya kasance yana da alhakin, da mun fita yanzu,' in ji shi.
Dan majalisar wakilai na Wellingborough ya kara da cewa: 'Zan tsaya wa Brexit amma muna bukatar mu jefa Chequers.'
Da yake nuna adawarsa ga EU, ya ce: 'Ba mu yi yaƙe-yaƙe na duniya don zama masu biyayya ba.
Muna son mu yi dokokinmu a kasarmu.'
Mista Bone ya yi watsi da shawarwarin da ra'ayin jama'a ya canza tun lokacin da aka kada kuri'un 2016: 'Tunanin cewa mutanen Burtaniya sun canza tunaninsu kuma suna son kasancewa ba gaskiya bane.'
Tory Brexiteer Andrea Jenkyns shima yana cikin zanga-zangar, yana gaya wa manema labarai: 'Ina kawai cewa: Firayim Minista, saurari mutane.
'Chequers ba shi da farin jini ga jama'a, 'Yan adawa ba za su zabe shi ba, ba shi da farin ciki tare da jam'iyyarmu da masu fafutukarmu waɗanda ke yin tituna a zahiri kuma suka zaɓe mu a farko.
Don Allah a daina Chequers kuma fara sauraron. '
A cikin wani sako da ya nuna wa Mrs May, ta kara da cewa: 'Firai ministoci suna kiyaye ayyukansu idan sun cika alkawurran da suka yi.'
Mista Farage ya gaya wa 'yan siyasa masu zanga-zangar dole ne a sanya su "ji zafi" idan suna gab da cin amanar shawarar da aka yanke a zaben raba gardama na shekarar 2016.
'Yanzu wannan batun amana ne tsakaninmu - mutane - da rukuninmu na siyasa,' in ji shi.
'Suna kokarin cin amanar Brexit kuma muna nan a yau don gaya musu 'ba za mu bari ku ku tafi ba tare da yin hakan ba.'
A cikin wani sako ga taron jama'a masu himma ya kara da cewa: 'Ina son ku sa 'yan siyasarmu, wadanda ke gab da cin amanar Brexit, su ji zafi.
'Muna tattara sojojin jama'a na wannan kasa wanda ya ba mu nasara a Brexit kuma ba za mu huta ba har sai mun zama mai zaman kanta, mai mulkin kai, mai alfahari da Ingila.'
A halin yanzu, Remainers sun yi tafiya ta Birmingham kafin gudanar da taron sa'a biyu a tsakiyar gari.
Wasu 'yan gwagwarmaya sun yi ta ɗaga tutocin Tories Against Brexit bayan ƙaddamar da kungiyar a wannan karshen mako.
Dan takarar jam'iyyar Labour Lord Adonis ya yi ba'a ga 'yan ra'ayin mazan jiya kan matsalolin tsaro da suka fuskanta tare da aikace-aikacen jam'iyyar yayin da aka bude taron.
'Waɗannan mutane ne suka gaya mana cewa za su iya samun tsarin IT a wuri da duk fasahar don Kanada da ƙari, don iyakar da ba ta da matsala, don cinikin kyauta ba tare da iyakoki a Ireland ba,' in ji shi.
'Wannan abin dariya ne.
Babu wani abu kamar mai kyau Brexit, "ya kara da cewa.
Warren na shirin yin 'dubawa sosai' wajen tsayawa takarar shugaban kasa
'Yar majalisar dattijai Elizabeth Warren ta ce za ta "yi kokari wajen tsayawa takarar shugaban kasa" bayan zaben Nuwamba.
Jaridar Boston Globe ta ruwaito cewa 'yar jam'iyyar Democrat ta Massachusetts ta yi magana game da makomarta a lokacin wani taron gari a yammacin Massachusetts ranar Asabar.
Warren, wanda ke yawan sukar Shugaba Donald Trump, yana neman sake zabarsa a watan Nuwamba a kan GOP na jihar Geoff Diehl, wanda shi ne shugaban shugaban kungiyar Trump na shekarar 2016 na Massachusetts.
Ta kasance a tsakiyar hasashen cewa za ta iya ɗaukar Trump a cikin 2020.
Taron da aka yi a yammacin Asabar a Holyoke shi ne karo na 36 da ta yi da masu zabe ta amfani da tsarin zauren gari tun lokacin da Trump ya hau karagar mulki.
Wani da ya halarci taron ya tambaye ta ko tana shirin tsayawa takarar shugaban kasa.
Warren ya amsa cewa lokaci ya yi "ga mata su je Washington don gyara gwamnatinmu da ta lalace, kuma wannan ya haɗa da mace a saman".
