Shugaba Donald Trump ya yi ba'a ga Sanata Dianne Feinstein a wani gangami a ranar Asabar kan dagewarta cewa ba ta fallasa wasikar daga Christine Blasey Ford ba tana zargin dan takarar Kotun Koli Brett Kavanaugh da cin zarafin jima'i.
Da yake magana a wani taro a Yammacin Virginia, shugaban bai yi magana kai tsaye game da shaidar da Ford ya bayar a gaban Kwamitin Shari'a na Majalisar Dattawa ba, maimakon haka ya yi sharhi cewa abin da ke faruwa a Majalisar Dattawa ya nuna cewa mutane "masu mugunta ne da munanan abubuwa da kuma karya".
"Abu daya da zai iya faruwa kuma abu mai kyau da ke faruwa a cikin 'yan kwanakin nan a Majalisar Dattawa, lokacin da kuka ga fushi, lokacin da kuka ga mutanen da suke fushi da ma'ana da mummuna da rashin gaskiya", in ji shi.
"Idan ka duba a saki da kuma leaks sa'an nan kuma suka ce "oh, ban yi ba.
Ni ban yi ba".
Ka tuna?
Dianne Feinstein, kin yi leak?
Ka tuna da amsar da ta bayar... ka fallasa takardar - "oh, oh, me?
Oh, a'a, ba haka ba ne.
Ban yi ruwa ba".
