Da yake ci gaba da kare shi na wanda aka zaba a kotun koli, wanda aka zarge shi da cin zarafin mata uku, shugaban ya nuna cewa 'yan Democrat suna amfani da zargin ne don nasu manufofin.
"Sun ƙudura niyyar sake karɓan iko ta kowace hanya da ta dace.
Kun ga ƙazanta, ƙazanta, ba su damu da wanda suka cutar ba, wanda dole ne su gudu don samun iko da iko, "Mediaite ya ruwaito shugaban yana cewa.
Wasannin Wasannin Elite: Dundee Stars 5-3 Belfast Giants
Patrick Dwyer ya ci kwallo biyu a ragar Giants da Dundee
Dundee Stars sun yi kafara don rashin nasarar da suka yi a gasar Elite League a ranar Juma'a da Belfast Giants ta hanyar lashe wasan dawowa 5-3 a Dundee a ranar Asabar.
Giants sun sami nasarar cin kwallaye biyu ta hanyar buga Patrick Dwyer da Francis Beauvillier.
Mike Sullivan da Jordan Cownie sun kawo matakin gida kafin Dwyer ya dawo da jagorancin Giants.
Francois Bouchard ya daidaita wa Dundee kafin kwallaye biyu na Lukas Lundvald Nielsen suka tabbatar da nasarar su.
Wannan shi ne kashi na uku na gasar Elite League na kakar wasa ta 'yan Adam Adam Keefe, wadanda suka zo daga baya don doke Dundee 2-1 a Belfast a daren Juma'a.
Ya kasance taro na huɗu na kakar tsakanin ɓangarorin, tare da Giants da suka ci wasannin uku na baya.
Dwyer ya buɗe a minti na huɗu a 3:35 daga Kendall McFaull ya taimaka, tare da David Rutherford yana ba da taimako yayin da Beauvillier ya ninka jagoranci minti hudu daga baya.
A cikin abin da ya kasance lokacin budewa, Sullivan ya kawo gida a cikin wasan a 13:10 kafin Matt Marquardt ya zama mai ba da gudummawa ga Cownie na daidaitawa a 15:16.
Dwyer ya tabbatar da cewa Giants sun jagoranci a farkon hutu lokacin da ya buga kwallo na biyu na dare a ƙarshen lokaci na farko.
Gidan gida ya sake sakewa kuma Bouchard ya sake sanya su a kan daidaito tare da burin wasan iko a 27:37.
Cownie da Charles Corcoran sun haɗu don taimakawa Nielsen ya ba Dundee jagora a karon farko a wasan a ƙarshen lokaci na biyu kuma ya tabbatar da nasarar da tawagarsa ta biyar ta shiga cikin rabin lokaci na ƙarshe.
Giants, wadanda yanzu sun yi rashin nasara hudu daga cikin wasanni biyar da suka gabata, suna gida ne da Milton Keynes a wasan su na gaba a ranar Juma'a.
Mai kula da zirga-zirgar jiragen sama ya mutu don tabbatar da cewa daruruwan mutane a cikin jirgin sama zasu iya tserewa girgizar kasa
An yi wa wani mai kula da zirga-zirgar jiragen sama a Indonesia yabo a matsayin gwarzo bayan da ya mutu yana tabbatar da cewa jirgin da ke dauke da daruruwan mutane ya tashi lafiya.
Sama da mutane 800 ne suka mutu kuma da yawa sun bace bayan da wata babbar girgizar kasa ta afkawa tsibirin Sulawesi a ranar Juma'a, inda ta haifar da tsunami.
Girgizar kasa mai karfi ta ci gaba da addabar yankin kuma mutane da yawa suna cikin tarkace a cikin birni na Palu.
Amma duk da abokan aikinsa suna guduwa don rayukansu, Anthonius Gunawan Agung mai shekaru 21 ya ƙi barin matsayinsa a hasumiyar sarrafawa da ke ta birgima a filin jirgin saman Mutiara Sis Al Jufri Palu.
Ya tsaya a wurin don tabbatar da cewa jirgin Batik Air Flight 6321, wanda yake kan titin jirgin a lokacin, ya sami damar tashi lafiya.
Sai ya yi tsalle daga hasumiyar kula da zirga-zirga lokacin da ya yi tunanin cewa tana rushewa.
Ya mutu daga baya a asibiti.
Kakakin Hukumar Kula da Jiragen Sama na Indonesia, Yohannes Sirait, ya ce wannan shawarar wataƙila ta ceci rayuka da yawa, in ji ABC News na Australia.
Mun shirya wani jirgin sama daga Balikpapan a Kalimantan don mu kai shi wani babban asibiti a wani birni.
Abin takaici mun rasa shi da safiyar yau kafin helikofta ya isa Palu.
