Hadarin jirgin saman Micronesia: Air Niugini yanzu ya ce an rasa mutum daya bayan hadarin jirgin saman lagoon
Kamfanin jirgin saman da ya yi hatsari a cikin wani tafkin Pacific a Micronesia yanzu ya ce an rasa mutum daya, bayan da ya ce duk fasinjoji 47 da ma'aikatan jirgin sun kwashe jirgin da ke nutsewa cikin aminci.
Kamfanin Air Niugini ya ce a cikin wata sanarwa cewa a ranar Asabar da yamma, ba zai iya ba da lissafin wani fasinja namiji ba.
Kamfanin jirgin ya ce yana aiki tare da hukumomin yankin, asibitoci da masu bincike don kokarin gano mutumin.
Kamfanin jirgin bai amsa nan da nan ba ga buƙatun don ƙarin bayani game da fasinja, kamar shekarunsa ko asalinsa.
Jiragen ruwa na gida sun taimaka wajen ceto sauran fasinjoji da ma'aikatan jirgin bayan jirgin ya buga ruwa yayin da yake kokarin sauka a filin jirgin saman Chuuk Island.
Jami'ai sun ce a ranar Juma'a cewa an kai mutane bakwai asibiti.
Kamfanin jirgin ya ce fasinjoji shida sun kasance a asibiti a ranar Asabar, kuma dukkansu suna cikin kwanciyar hankali.
Abin da ya haifar da hadarin da kuma ainihin jerin abubuwan da suka faru ya kasance ba a sani ba.
Kamfanin jirgin da kuma rundunar sojan Amurka sun ce jirgin ya sauka a cikin tafkin da ke kusa da titin jirgin.
Wasu shaidu sun yi tunanin cewa jirgin ya yi sama da titin jirgin.
Baƙon Ba'amurke Bill Jaynes ya ce jirgin ya zo ne a ƙasa sosai.
Jaynes ya ce: "Wannan abu ne mai kyau ƙwarai".
