Turai ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup a Paris
Team Turai ta lashe gasar cin kofin Ryder ta 2018 ta doke Team USA da ƙimar 16.5 zuwa 10.5 a Le Golf National a wajen Paris, Faransa.
Amurka ta yi asara sau shida a jere a kan Turai kuma ba ta lashe gasar Ryder a Turai ba tun 1993.
Turai ta sake samun kambin ne yayin da tawagar kyaftin din Denmark Thomas Bjorn ta kai maki 14.5 da suke bukata don doke Amurka.
Tauraron Amurka Phil Mickelson, wanda ya yi gwagwarmaya a mafi yawan gasar, ya jefa harbinsa a cikin ruwa a rami na 16, ya kuma yi nasara da Francesco Molinari.
Dan wasan Italiya Molinari ya haskaka a duk wasanninsa, ya zama daya daga cikin 'yan wasa 4 da suka taba yin 5-0-0 tun lokacin da aka fara gasar a shekarar 1979.
Ba'amurke Jordan Spieth ya busa 5 & 4 daga mafi ƙarancin ɗan wasa a cikin ƙungiyar Turai, Thorbjorn Olesen na Denmark.
Dan wasan da ya fi kowa daraja a duniya, Dustin Johnson, ya fadi 2 da 1 a hannun Ian Poulter na Ingila wanda zai iya buga wasansa na karshe a gasar Ryder.
Tsohon ɗan wasan Ryder Cup takwas, ɗan Spain Sergio Garcia ya zama gasar da ta fi cin nasara a Turai tare da maki 25.5 a cikin aikinsa.
"Ba na yawan yin kuka amma yau ba zan iya yin hakan ba.
Shekara ce mai wuya.
Ina godiya da Thomas ya zaɓe ni kuma ya gaskata da ni.
Ina farin ciki, farin ciki don dawo da kofin.
Wannan game da kungiyar ne, kuma ina farin cikin na iya taimakawa, "in ji Garcia mai cike da motsin rai bayan nasarar Turai.
Ya ba da wutar ga ɗan'uwansa John Ram wanda ya kori tsohon dan wasan golf na Amurka Tiger Woods 2 & 1 a wasan wasa a ranar Lahadi.
"Girman kai da nake ji, na doke Tiger Woods, na girma ina kallon wannan mutumin", in ji Rahm mai shekara 23.
Woods ya rasa dukkan wasanninsa hudu a Faransa kuma yanzu yana da rikodin 13-21-3 na aikin Ryder Cup.
Wani abin mamaki da ya faru da daya daga cikin manyan 'yan wasa a duk lokacin, ya lashe manyan lakabi 14 na biyu ga Jack Nicklaus.
Team USA sun yi gwagwarmaya duk karshen mako don neman fairways tare da banda Patrick Reed, Justin Thomas da Tony Finau, wadanda suka buga wasan golf mai girma a cikin dukkan gasar.
