Sabuntawar Red Tide: Matsakaicin ya ragu a Pinellas, Manatee da Sarasota
Sabon rahoto daga Hukumar Kifi da Dabbobi ta Florida ya nuna raguwar yawan Red Tide a wasu sassan yankin Tampa Bay.
A cewar FWC, ana ba da rahoton yanayin fure na patchier a yankunan Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da Collier counties - wanda ke nuna raguwar maida hankali.
Ruwan Farin Ruwan ya kai kimanin kilomita 130 na bakin teku daga arewacin Pinellas zuwa kudancin Lee.
Za a iya samun wuraren da ke da nisan mil 10 daga gabar tekun Hillsborough County, amma a wurare da yawa da suka shafi makon da ya gabata.
An kuma lura da Red Tide a cikin Gundumar Pasco.
An bayar da rahoton matsakaici a cikin ko kuma daga bakin rairayin bakin teku na Pinellas County a cikin makon da ya gabata, ƙananan ƙananan zuwa ƙananan ƙananan a bakin teku na Hillsborough County, bayanan zuwa ga babban taro a cikin Manatee County, bayanan zuwa manyan taro a cikin ko daga bakin teku na Sarasota County, bayanan zuwa matsakaici a cikin Charlotte County, bayanan zuwa manyan taro a cikin ko daga bakin teku na Lee County, da ƙananan ƙananan a cikin Collier County.
Ana ci gaba da bayar da rahoton cutar numfashi a cikin Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee, da kuma Collier counties.
Ba a ba da rahoton cutar numfashi ba a Arewa maso yammacin Florida a cikin makon da ya gabata.
